OL,6,FA disabled retired nurse has spoken of
OL,7,Fhis distress at getting daily ULEZ
OL,8,Ffines despite being granted an
OL,9,Fexemption.JFrankie McDonald, 67, of
OL,10,FEdmonton, north London was give a blue
OL,11,Fbadge exemption on February 1st.JBut
OL,12,Fhe has since been sent four Penalty
OL,13,FCharge Notices, each one demanding
OL,14,F#180, reduced to #90 if paid within 14
OL,15,Fdays.JTransport for London has told
OL,16,Fhim a fifth PCN is in the post.
