OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News London Frankie
OL,7,Fsaid: "The car is my only mode of
OL,8,Ftransport, and because of my
OL,9,Fdisability - I broke my back when I
OL,10,Ffell down the stairs - I really need
OL,11,Fmy car to get about and to just to
OL,12,Fconduct my daily living in London.
OL,13,F"And it's terrifying because the
OL,14,Fcharges are #180 or #90 if you pay it
OL,15,Fwithin 14 days.J"As an elderly
OL,16,Fgentleman living on as an old age
OL,17,Fpensioner I don't have the money to
OL,18,Fpay TfL.
